cs.RO, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.CV, cs.SY

Reasoning: 
- cs.RO (Robotics) is the most likely category as the paper deals with developing control policies for robots in simulation and transferring them to the real world. 
- cs.LG (Machine Learning) is also likely as the paper proposes a deep inverse dynamics model to decide which real-world action is most suitable to achieve the next states. 
- cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is relevant as the paper uses reinforcement learning to obtain policies in simulation. 
- cs.CV (Computer Vision) is less likely but still possible as the paper may involve vision-based simulations or real-world experiments. 
- cs.SY (Systems and Control) is also less likely but possible as the paper deals with control policies for robots.
